Package: aisdk.skills
Title: Skill Authoring, Store, and Bundled Skill Pack for 'aisdk'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yonghe", "Xia", , "xiayh17@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Skill-ecosystem tooling and content for the 'aisdk' toolkit:
    scaffolding helpers for authoring new skills, a global skill store for
    sharing and installing skills, skill-forge authoring tools, and a bundled
    pack of ready-to-use skills. On load it registers its bundled skill
    directory with the core 'aisdk' skill registry, so the core skill-loading
    runtime stays free of this content.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: aisdk (>= 1.4.12), httr2, rlang, yaml, jsonlite, R6, base64enc, utils
Suggests: withr, curl, testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/YuLab-SMU/aisdk.skills
BugReports: https://github.com/YuLab-SMU/aisdk.skills/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
